{"tid":2031004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（仲唔快d調佢老未？）【民建聯國安法問卷調查】","createTime":"2020-05-23T06:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T07:22:57.000Z","uid":108359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa35099f0d12bbbe77a33a9f6c317482e93ce55","tid":2031004,"uid":108359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"【民建聯國安法問卷調查】<br />\n<br />\n第十三屆全國人大三次會議的議程包括審議「港版國安法」，草案主要針對四類行為，包括顛覆國家政權、分裂國家、恐怖活動，以及外部勢力干預。<br />\n<br />\n現在民建聯正就港版國安法進行一份問卷調查，請大家廣傳出去，並邀請填寫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wj.qq.com/s2/6367853/3622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwj.qq.com%2Fs2%2F6367853%2F3622&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOXWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=57192579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wj.qq.com/s2/6367853/3622</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1H6M1J8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1H6M1J8.png&h=8519b499&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ce5762af8087cb9a997aa35a4e302e298c0eb07","tid":2031004,"uid":231886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"咪撚做，report都無用<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">系统由腾讯问卷提供</span><br />\n岩岩中伏入左去，已經記錄左ip"},{"pid":"d543a1a7d361ceb0902554473e9b236ff554244e","tid":2031004,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">見到個website都唔會㩒落去啦下嘛</span>"},{"pid":"d6ef5661ea291a8f5383a90000feb776b7f173c5","tid":2031004,"uid":48081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:14:30.000Z","msg":"緊急要人！開埋vpn先好做 民建聯國安法問卷調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2030676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2030676</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1ed12230aefc7fd74b89c34606232332bf0ac27","tid":2031004,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"on9先click<br />\n送頭"},{"pid":"39b2701bc9705c476cabf2